## 📈 Revenue Projections (3-Year)

### Conservative Scenario

| Period | Monthly Revenue | Annual Revenue | Key Drivers |
|--------|----------------|----------------|-------------|
| **Month 1-3** | ₹0-5K | — | Building userbase, free features |
| **Month 4-6** | ₹15K-40K | — | Affiliate links live, newsletter sponsors |
| **Month 7-12** | ₹50K-1.5L | **₹6-12L** | Pro subscriptions + sponsored placements |
| **Year 2** | ₹2-5L/mo | **₹24-60L** | B2B API + white-label + scale |
| **Year 3** | ₹8-20L/mo | **₹96L-2.4Cr** | Full monetization, 200K+ MAU |

### Optimistic Scenario (with funding/partnerships)

| Period | Monthly Revenue | Annual Revenue |
|--------|----------------|----------------|
| **Year 1** | ₹1-3L/mo | **₹12-36L** |
| **Year 2** | ₹5-15L/mo | **₹60L-1.8Cr** |
| **Year 3** | ₹25-50L/mo | **₹3-6Cr** |

### Unit Economics

| Metric | Free User | Pro User |
|--------|-----------|----------|
| **CAC** (Customer Acquisition Cost) | ₹30-80 | ₹200-500 |
| **LTV** (Lifetime Value) | ₹50-150 (affiliate) | ₹2,500-5,000 |
| **LTV:CAC Ratio** | 1.5-2x | **5-10x** ⭐ |
| **Monthly AI Cost** | ₹0 (Gemini free tier) | ₹0 (Gemini free tier) |
| **Gross Margin** | ~85% | ~92% |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **AI cost is essentially ₹0** thanks to Gemini 2.0 Flash free tier (15 RPM, 1M tokens/min). This gives us an insane margin advantage over competitors using GPT-4.

