## 🛡️ Competitive Moat

| Moat | PayWise | Competitors (CRED, Curation) |
|------|---------|------|
| **AI Personal Assistant** | ✅ Gemini-powered chat | ❌ None |
| **Cross-App Comparison** | ✅ 9 payment apps | ❌ Single app focus |
| **Cost** | ₹0 AI cost (Gemini free) | $$$$ GPT-4 costs |
| **Savings Tracking** | ✅ Automated + AI | ❌ Manual |
| **India-First** | ✅ UPI, ₹, local apps | ❌ Global focus |
| **DPDP Compliance** | ✅ Built-in | ❌ Afterthought |
| **No RBI License Needed** | ✅ Info only, no payments | ❌ Payment processors need licenses |

