## ⚠️ Risks & Mitigations

| Risk | Likelihood | Mitigation |
|------|-----------|------------|
| Supabase India blocking | HIGH (happening now) | VPN workaround, plan migration to PlanetScale/Neon |
| Low initial user acquisition | MEDIUM | SEO + content marketing + Product Hunt launch |
| Gemini API rate limits at scale | LOW | Free tier is generous (15 RPM); upgrade to paid at ₹0.01/query |
| Offer data staleness | MEDIUM | Build auto-scraping pipeline (Priority 2) |
| Competitor copying AI features | LOW | First-mover advantage + user data moat |

